# Copy to .env (gitignored) and fill in values for local dev.
# Astro reads everything matching VITE_* into client bundles, and
# everything else into the Node build context. Keep secrets out of
# VITE_* — anything prefixed with VITE_ ships to the browser.

# Stripe test-mode Secret Key — sk_test_…
# Get from Stripe Dashboard (test mode) → Developers → API keys.
# Used at BUILD TIME by web/src/lib/pricing.ts to look up the
# `boltmate_lifetime` Price. Absent → loadPricing() falls back to the
# hard-coded default so the site still builds.
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_PASTE_YOUR_TEST_KEY_HERE
